trong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/6dd666b11d0030c8e6cb15ae6dfb0f0e.poster.avif?t=1627473941\" width=608 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/6dd666b11d0030c8e6cb15ae6dfb0f0e.webm?t=1627473941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/6dd666b11d0030c8e6cb15ae6dfb0f0e.mp4?t=1627473941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build, blow up, and destroy! In this world of realistic physics, you can smash castles with catapults, blow up buildings, shoot slingshots and throw objects, and watch buildings fall apart beautifully.<br><br>This is a true destruction simulator. Create your own building from scratch, or choose from one of the available options. Decide in which mode you want to demolish it - by completing tasks or creating chaos with various tools in the sandbox and get down to the fun, or take your time and tear down piece by piece.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/293f662dd44c1bcdc20a314bb65a6d47.poster.avif?t=1627473941\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/293f662dd44c1bcdc20a314bb65a6d47.webm?t=1627473941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/293f662dd44c1bcdc20a314bb65a6d47.mp4?t=1627473941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simulate physics using the latest <strong>Unreal Engine Chaos</strong> technology.<br></li><li>Beautifully realistic destruction.<br></li><li>Sandbox with a variety of destructive tools.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/e38a1da1cd5c43a1b3fe38ac838ebe49.poster.avif?t=1627473941\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/e38a1da1cd5c43a1b3fe38ac838ebe49.webm?t=1627473941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/e38a1da1cd5c43a1b3fe38ac838ebe49.mp4?t=1627473941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
