alistic destruction.<br></li><li>Sandbox with a variety of destructive tools.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/e38a1da1cd5c43a1b3fe38ac838ebe49.poster.avif?t=1627473941\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/e38a1da1cd5c43a1b3fe38ac838ebe49.webm?t=1627473941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1666660/extras/e38a1da1cd5c43a1b3fe38ac838ebe49.mp4?t=1627473941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
